fields.inlineHelpText: Compare a numeric service property with a numeric resource property
fields.label: Boolean Operator
fields.name: FSL__Boolean_Operator__c

fields.inlineHelpText:
Determines the length of the breaks created. 
Leave this field empty if you don't want to create breaks.
fields.label: Break Duration (minutes)
fields.name: FSL__Break_Duration__c

fields.inlineHelpText:
Determines the minimum break start time (in the format: {HH:MM}) to create breaks. 
Leave this field empty if you don't want to create breaks.
fields.label: Break Start
fields.name: FSL__Break_Start__c

fields.inlineHelpText: If checked, gap between services will be based on the minimum gap field, without travel calculations.
fields.label: Fixed Gap
fields.name: FSL__Is_Fixed_Gap__c

fields.inlineHelpText: Determines what distance or how many minutes the resource can travel from home to reach a service
fields.label: Maximum Travel From Home
fields.name: FSL__Maximum_Travel_From_Home__c

fields.inlineHelpText: Determines the minimum gap between services. If fixed gap is enabled, determines the gap between the services.
fields.label: Minimum Gap (minutes)
fields.name: FSL__Minimum_Gap__c

fields.inlineHelpText:
Determines how many minutes prior to the resource's calendar start of day will be available for travel (on the resource's expense).
When empty, any amount of travel prior to start of work day is valid.
fields.label: Travel From Home (minutes)
fields.name: FSL__Travel_From_Home__c

fields.inlineHelpText:
Determines how many minutes following the resource's calendar end of day will be available for travel (on the resource's expense).
When empty, any amount of travel following the end of work day is valid.
fields.label: Travel To Home (minutes)
fields.name: FSL__Travel_To_Home__c

fields.inlineHelpText:
When checked, compare the Minimum Crew Size field on the Work Order or Work Order Line Item to the actual available Service Crew Members. 
Otherwise, compare the Minimum Crew Size to the Crew Size field on the Service Crew.
fields.label: Consider Service Crew Membership
fields.name: FSL__Crew_Resources_Availability__c
